ents/number-field#aria-and-labeling","content":"Set &#x2A;*`isWheelDisabled`** if the value should not change when the user scrolls with a pointer wheel while the field is focused."},"581":{"id":"/docs/components/number-field-31","page_id":"/docs/components/number-field","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/number-field#best-practices","content":"Pair &#x2A;*`isInvalid`*&#x2A; with &#x2A;*`errorMessage`** so users get both visual and programmatic feedback."},"582":{"id":"/docs/components/number-field-32","page_id":"/docs/components/number-field","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/number-field#best-practices","content":"Remember valid steps start from &#x2A;*`minValue`**."},"583":{"id":"/docs/components/number-field-33","page_id":"/docs/components/number-field","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/number-field#best-practices","content":"Use &#x2A;*`isDisabled`*&#x2A; when the value cannot be changed; use &#x2A;*`isReadOnly`** when the value should be visible but not editable. Do not use them interchangeably."},"584":{"id":"/docs/components/number-field-34","page_id":"/docs/components/number-field","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/number-field#best-practices","content":"For currency or units, ensure &#x2A;*`formatOptions`** (and locale) match what users are allowed to type."},"585":{"id":"/docs/components/pagination","page_id":"/docs/components/pagination","type":"page","content":"Pagination","breadcrumbs":["Docs","Components"],"tags":[],"url":"/docs/components/pagination"},"586":{"id":"/docs/components/pagination-0","page_id":"/docs/components/pagination","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/pagination","content":"A pagination component with prev/next buttons and dot indicators, configurable page limits, and optional visibility of controls and dots"},"587":{"id":"/docs/components/pagination-1","page_id":"/docs/components/pagination","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/components/pagination#installation"